binding.p: The various pamphlets are held in a single paper folder ( 235 176 ) labelled I & J.

The entirety of Acc. 4 c I[1-14] were originally wrapped in a paper cover measuring approximately 380 250 when unfolded. On this paper cover, which is highly fragile and damaged around the edges, is written Access 4 C I. Mapper med A-B, E-P.

The manuscript is currently held in a modern archival paper folder measuring
305 215 .
Acc. 4 c I[1-7] are all held in an archival box measuring 320 230 75

msItem.explicit: meg yvir tann unga Ribar Ulv at hevna

msItem.title: Commentary
msItem.author: V. U. Hammershaimb
msItem.incipit: Sandt at sige, gider jeg ikke skrive den af på færøsk, da den slet ikke er færøsk
msItem.explicit: da to og få jo også rime sammen i den danske v. 26.
msItem.note: Letter to Svend Grundtvig, dated Kirketeig (Kirkjuteigur parsonage in Kvívík), 4 December 1858.

condition.p: The paper is in fragil condition, with damage and curling at the edges.

additions.p: On the back the notes (cf. O Effersøes opt. 1846 Corp. XIII, 361) and (v. 1-8 aldeles ens) have been added.

Gár í dans frúir! sprund

dansa med við hánd
so fàgurliga sum tú kan,
gár í dans frúir!
